description: President Recep Tayyip Erdogan of Turkey said that he would have a meeting with members of his Parliament on Tuesday to go over the details of the journalist Jamal Khashoggi’s killing at the Saudi Consulate in Istanbul.
title: ‘We Are Seeking Justice,’ Turkish President Says of Khashoggi Case
